Items.r: 【以藤蔓代梯子進入谷底...我身上的{color=#FF0000}朱雀令{/color}上寫到的{color=#FF0000}崖底{/color}，應該就是這裡了，趕緊看看此處藏了些什麼祕密。】
Items.c: <[>以藤蔓代梯子進入谷底...我身上的朱雀令上寫到的崖底,應該就是這裡了,趕緊看看此處藏了些什麼祕密。<]>
Items.mt: <[>Taking a vine instead of a ladder to get to the bottom of the valley... I think this is the bottom of the cliff written on the Vermilion Bird Order I'm carrying, so let's see what secrets are hidden here. <]>
